Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:02.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all started with the Sacred Tree.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.99,0:00:04.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fighting and searching\nforourdreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:06.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a strong bond\nis formed between us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:07.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new hope!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:09.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bright future begins now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:11.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At last, the path is opened.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:12.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In pursuit of Naraku,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:15.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}we enterthe borderthat separates\nthis world from the afterlife.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:17.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the graveyard where\NInuyasha's fatheralso sleeps,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:19.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the guard of the Sacred Jewel shard\nlies in wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:21.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final shard guides us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:22.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the other side of the well,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:24.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a new day awaits in\nthe age of warring states!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:25.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:26.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:07.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll swallow you up in one gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:09.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:17.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:25.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:29.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He takes every advantage\nof them, {\i1}then....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:34.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, weren't you planning\nto defeat Princess Abi, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:37.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:40.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks to me, you all {\i1}are....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:45.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,now able to go to the border\nbetween this world and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The time has come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He cut off Tekkei's {\i1}head....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:28.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A river of {\i1}blood....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:32.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This connects to the border between\nthis world and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:41.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:48.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This river of blood\nwill not last.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I don't need to\nbe told that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:52.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:54.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:55.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:05.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's no good, Master Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:06.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:10.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you {\i1}are{\i0} able to get to\nthe border on this current,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:12.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,how do you intend\nto come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:14.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:16.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,even Naraku has\nthe same problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:19.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to be\nworrying about how to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:20.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's exactly what I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:22.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:31.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can see things that\nlook like human faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:32.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:34.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These {\i1}are....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:38.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,probably the feelings of resentment\nof the people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:42.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,whose blood Princess Abi's mother,\NTekkei, drank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How many people were {\i1}killed....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:48.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,just so he could get his\nhands on the Sacred Jewel shard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to bring this to\nan end quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:53.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:01.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yayakoshi yo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:02.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yoyoko...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:03.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru,\nwhat could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:09.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru,\nit's a giant bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:12.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ho! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is headless!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:19.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That scent of a massive amount\nof blood has disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:21.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:24.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems you were too late,\NSesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:27.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The entry way has closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:28.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:29.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:31.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what are you up to anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:35.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've been showing up a lot\naround Lord Sesshomaru lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:38.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru isn't\nthe least bit interested in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:39.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or....maybe he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:44.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean\nby "entry way"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm... How unusual...\nhe's taken the bait.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To the path that leads to\nthe border
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,between this world\nand the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku and Inuyasha\nhave already gone through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From yourmanner of speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:58.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it seems that you\nknow something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:00.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I doknow something {\i1}else....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:02.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About anotherpath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:05.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although Sesshomaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:08.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,even you may not be able\nto cross that path alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's happening?\NSomething seems wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:20.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A light!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:21.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:25.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:44.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:47.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:06.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Man, we could have been\nblown away, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:13.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Isn't {\i1}this....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:14.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:16.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:27.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the borderbetween this world\nand the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:31.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademon {\i1}graveyard....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:33.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that Inuyasha's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:35.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so {\i1}huge....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:45.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This isn't the time\nforleisurely sightseeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:52.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku got here before us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:53.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:56.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn that Naraku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:58.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He probably intends to lay low{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}until Kagome finds\nthe Sacred Jewel shard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:06.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can sense the Sacred Jewel shard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:08.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:10.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:11.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:12.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:00.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:04.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:06.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:07.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:09.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all {\i1}right....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:10.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You suddenly lost\nconsciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:13.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that just now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:16.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I thinking about\nthat time now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:19.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:20.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! Don't worry about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:43.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These are shining spears!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:46.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! We'll be skewered!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:48.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this Naraku's doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:54.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! These are adamantite!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Adamantite?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:57.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like diamonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Daiyamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:01.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never heard of such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the hardest jewel\nin this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:07.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These spears are made\nof adamantite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:08.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But {\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't sense\NNaraku's ghostly aura at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:14.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then who the hell is\nbehind this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:20.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The spears are shooting out\nof my old man's grave!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:23.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:27.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The light spears have stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:34.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:39.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0} The Sacred Jewel\nshard is in yourfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:39.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are not dead men, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:02.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are grave robbers\nafterthe Sacred Jewel shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:03.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:09.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Making a nest in the belly\nof someone's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:13.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Father," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:22.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you saying you're the son\nof the Great Dog Demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:24.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master {\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:27.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This skull...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:29.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could it be Hosenki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:31.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you Hosenki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's me, Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hosenki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:39.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one who made the black\npearl for Inuyasha long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:41.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:45.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then this young one\nmust be Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:49.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha is not your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:54.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Without a doubt, I made the black\npearl at your father's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:56.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, Inuyasha,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:12:00.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you passed through the black pearl\nonce to come to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:05.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Having fulfilled its purpose,\nthe black pearl has lost its power
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:08.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and returned to its place\nin yourrighteye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:09.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was it {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who made me see those visions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Visions?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:18.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those were probably thoughts\nstill left in the black pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In the black pearl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:24.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't the visions you had\ntell you to leave this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:28.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It goes without saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:31.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,entering the land of the dead\nagain is not {\i1}allowed....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:33.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:36.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ahh....Umm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:38.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:41.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hosenki has the Sacred Jewel shard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:46.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you bring the\NSacred Jewel shard here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:49.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? So you have it, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:52.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hand it overpeacefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:54.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you do, we'll go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:55.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:59.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is because it was\nthis Sacred Jewel shard's will
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to come to the land of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The shard's will?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:11.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am the demon who controls jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I have the powerto\nheartheir will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:17.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I existed in\nthe land of humans
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:19.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and my life was nearing\nthe end,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:23.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a Sacred Jewel shard came\ninto my possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the shard spoke to me\nand said that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:29.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Sacred Jewel must never\nbe allowed to become whole again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:34.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Most of the Sacred Jewel shards\nare in the possession of evil men
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:36.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and are tainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if it were to become\nmixed with those,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:41.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,my shard would also\nbecome tainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that is precisely why
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:45.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must keep it here in\nthis demon grave
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:48.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,beyond the reach of\nthe hands of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:53.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was the Sacred Jewel shard's\ndesire to come with me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:59.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha, it would be\nwise to back off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:02.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave the shard to {\i1}Hosenki....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:05.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Are you half-asleep\nor something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:08.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku has already come\nto this world ahead of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's hiding somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,waiting forhis chance\nto get the Sacred Jewel shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:24.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter who comes,\NI shall not let him have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:27.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Hosenki, {\i1}you....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:34.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:35.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:37.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is no ordinary happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:52.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall not go easy\non you either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wait Hosenki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me {\i1}explain....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, you stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:18.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:21.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you! Betterlearn to tell\nthe difference
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:23.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,between friend and foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:29.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga isn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:31.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless, Master Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hosenki's arms are hardened\nadamantite!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:38.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old {\i1}Myoga....{\i0} When did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:38.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It only took a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:40.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:45.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's too reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:46.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He has nothing to\nland on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:51.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-Hosenki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you seriously trying to\nharm Inuyasha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sacred Jewel shard is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sacred Jewel shard is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:20.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be careful, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hosenki's Sacred Jewel shard\nhas turned black!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:24.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:26.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel shard turns\ngood orevil
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:30.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,depending on the heart\nof its possessor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From his story just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:37.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't think Hosenki brought the\nshard here out of personal greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sense the presence of\ntainted Sacred Jewel {\i1}shards....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:47.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The size of this {\i1}presence....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Naraku's!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:50.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So Naraku is influencing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:53.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:54.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is Naraku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:00.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The presence is all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:04.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't tell in which direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:06.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didja hearthat, Hosenki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you hang onto it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:12.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,your soul will be taken\nby the tainted shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give it up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:16.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:19.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am not so weak as to\nlose my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:21.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to a minorirritant such as this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:29.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will notgive it up\nto {\i1}anyone....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:33.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! I guess I have no choice\nbut to take it by force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:36.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Hosenki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before your soul is devoured,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:41.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take the Sacred Jewel shard\noutta you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:45.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take it if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His whole body is\nturning black.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:50.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It must be the evil from\nthe shard spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:53.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:56.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha,\ngo easy on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hosenki is an old\nfriend of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:01.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He is {\i1}not{\i0} a bad demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:04.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I could beat him easily,\NI'd do just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did it work?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:22.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:30.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:53.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... I will not run away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:58.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:18:59.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:09.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:12.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Wind Scarisn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:29.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to get close to\nthe shard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must stop Hosenki's attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:45.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can purify that shard...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:49.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My arrow will probably work...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:51.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:57.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:01.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... That was pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:02.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:05.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It didn't purify the shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even Kagome's arrow\nhad no effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:09.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The arrow didn't reach\nthe shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That body is like armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not only that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:17.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hosenki was a great demon\nwho lived for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome's arrow doesn't\nhave enough spiritual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:24.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So....the{\i0} spiritual power\nneeds to be stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:27.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If it's Kikyo's {\i1}arrow....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:32.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:37.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo's arrow rejected her?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give this to Kagome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:43.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But whethershe can use it\nfully ornot...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:45.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}will depend on Kagome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does it mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:50.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it impossible forKagome?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:51.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The spot that was hit\nby Kagome's arrow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:01.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}he's covering it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:05.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, aim for that spot\nonce more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:06.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}B-But....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:08.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry up and shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:09.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A-All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:13.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just because Kagome's arrow\ndidn't reach the shard,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.53,0:21:15.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}doesn't mean it had\nno effect at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:21.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'lljust cut it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:23.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:29.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It broke open!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:30.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now I can get the shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:37.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You....fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:38.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:43.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:54.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You and {\i1}I....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.53,0:21:58.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All of us were just made\nto dance by the black jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:21:59.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:04.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.31,0:23:49.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I finally possess the last of\nthe Sacred Jewel shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:51.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hosenki's shard is stolen\nby Naraku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.35,0:23:53.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's come sneaking out,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:54.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and that's what I've been\nwaiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:57.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sesshomaru is guided by Kagura\nto the site of the showdown!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.52,0:23:59.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you rush overto\nsave your youngerbrother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.89,0:24:02.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a kind brotheryou are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:05.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A half-demon like {\i1}you....{\i0}\ncorrupting my father's grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.77,0:24:06.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.03,0:24:09.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Final Battle at the Graveside:\NSesshomaru Versus Inuyasha!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.80,0:24:12.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The only one who can kill\NNaraku is Sesshomaru!
